      "detail": "Clause 8 establishes offences and fines. The AI Authority has powers to accredit auditors, require disclosure, and conduct gap analysis. The AI Responsible Officer creates a corporate escalation point. Together these form multi-level defined escalation: corporate officer to Authority to enforcement action. This exceeds the UK's current best-efforts AISI approach and matches the EU's standard."
    },
    "Command Actor": {
